{start_of_verse: Verse 5}
[C]Old Timer can't you see that scene that though the years go [G]by
[A7]Those babies all went on the job the same as you [D7]and I
[G]I know you're glad that things have changed [C]while we have lots of [G]fun
[D7]As we go in and do the jobs that babies used to [G]run
{end_of_verse}

